
                ChangeLog file for VideoEye


Changes in 0.3:
- Updated .gitignore with MFC project specific rules
- Created libs/ directory to store DLL files (prevents deletion during clean)
- Configured post-build events to automatically copy DLLs to output directory
- Removed unnecessary 32-bit related files and directories
- Removed .suo and .aps files from git tracking
- Added .gitignore file
- Fixed bugs
- Made some changes
- Fixed Chinese garbled characters issue

Changes in 0.2:
- Add Unicode Character Set Support
- Fixed "INT64_MIN INT64_MAX" Error
- Change CTreeCtrl in InputList Dialog
- Add data output function in Video Detail Analysis Dialog (QP,MBtype,MV.. can output as .csv file)
- Fix an error about MPEG4's motion vector analysis funcion in Video Detail Analysis Dialog
- Fix a bug in resize function of Video Window
